name: Finpay - UI Kit
description:
Finpay is a Premium and High-Quality Finance App UI Kit with 80 high-quality screens and easy to use in Figma. Available in Light & Dark theme.


The UI Kit is suitable and easy to fully customize for any kind app transaction/financial and banking related projects also the screens is usable for other product design as well.


The UI Kit leverages all Figma features, including design system, typography, iconography, dynamic components & variants.
